fields.value: General and Specific Self-report Health Measures (CAPS-HEALTH1 and CAPS-HEALTH2 module)

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This 120 item questionnaire obtains both general and specific self-report health measures. Included are an overall health rating, willingness to change lifestyle, alcohol use, smoking, exercise habits, eating habits, nutrition, happiness, concentration, stress measures, reactions to stress, illness and illness outcomes, and medication history.

In CAPS85 part of the unit was administered twice. The second administration is called HEALTH2

No standard scoring.
